1. Import the northwind_employees.csv file into power query from the datasets folder on the desktop
2. Perform a left join on the total sales query with the Employees query using EmployeeID as the common column in both tables
3. Expand the Employees column to include the Name and ReportsTo columns from the Employees query
- Make sure to uncheck "Use original column Name as prefix"
4. Perform another left join between the Total Sales and Employee queries
  This time joining the ReportsTo column in the Total Sales query with the employeeID column in the Employees table
5. Expand the Employees column to include Name. Rename Name.1 column to Manager Name
